divs: Sighting DetailsLooking at photos of Hawaii trip and noticed what looks like a UFO in three frames. I was in Hawaii the big Island. I think Heilo side taking pictures of sunset. I wasn't aware of the object until two weeks ago, looking at photos of Hawaii trip. I noticed something in the picture and zoomed in. WOW a UFO! I don't know if indeed this is a UFO and if it is, I don't know if it's man made or alien.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Hielo The big Island
